  "description": "<i>Game Boy Wars 3</i> is a turn based strategy game, it is the last game in the <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?quickSearch=Game+Boy+Wars\">Game Boy Wars</a> series for the Game Boy Color. The story is similar to previous games: the Red Star army fights against the White Moon army.<br><br>The goal is invariable, the player must destroy all enemy forces or capture the enemy's capital city. The player can buy various units - soldiers, vehicles, tanks, planes, helicopters, or boats. <i>Game Boy Wars 3</i> is more difficult than others games in the  series as the player must have facilities and materials to build new units. Battles and other actions like sieges are shown as short animated sequences.<br><br>The game has 60 maps in skirmishes (standard mode) and 45 campaign missions. <i>Game Boy Wars 3</i> also features a Beginner Mode",
